        <h1>
            Track Everything.<br>
            Understand Your Users.<br>
            Make Smarter Decisions.
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-text">
            We help businesses turn raw data into actionable insights.
            From website traffic to conversion tracking, we set up analytics
