            help you understand user behavior, optimize campaigns, and increase ROI
            through data-driven decisions.

        </p>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- BENEFITS -->

<section class="benefits">

    <div class="container">

        <h2 class="section-title">

            What You Get

        </h2>

        <div class="benefit-grid">

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-chart-line"></i>

                <h3>Website Tracking</h3>

                <p>
                    Monitor traffic, user behavior and engagement in real time.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-target"></i>

                <h3>Conversion Tracking</h3>

                <p>
                    Track leads, sales and form submissions accurately.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-brand-google"></i>

                <h3>Google Analytics Setup</h3>

                <p>
                    Proper GA4 setup for complete business insights.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-report-analytics"></i>

                <h3>Performance Reports</h3>

                <p>
                    Monthly reports to understand growth and performance.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-graph"></i>

                <h3>Data Insights</h3>

                <p>
                    Clear insights to improve marketing and product decisions.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-device-analytics"></i>

